v 3
d owatable: Word table for three-group Welch one-way ANOVA
d
d owatable creates a compact Word table for multiple outcomes compared
d across exactly three groups using Welch one-way ANOVA, Benjamini-Hochberg
d FDR q-values, Games-Howell pairwise comparisons, and Hedges' g_av.
d Block headings may be supplied with blockfile() or parsed from variable
d labels with blockfromlabel.
d
d Author: Hao Ma
d Version: 1.0.0, 26jun2026
d
